  <brief_title>The Prevention of Postoperative Epidural Catheter Migration: a Comparison of Three Types of Dressing</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Prevention of Postoperative Epidural Catheter Migration: a Comparison of Three Types of Dressing</official_title>
  <sponsors>
